about.summary: Robust Location and Scatter Estimation and Robust Multivariate Analysis with High Breakdown Point.

name: r-rrcov
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.4-7' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rrcov
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/rrcov_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/rrcov/rrcov_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: cbd08ccce8b583a2f88946a3267c8fc494ee2b44ba749b9296a6e3d818f6f293

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 2
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('fortran') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_fortran') }}  # [win]
    - {{posix}}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{posix}}make
    - {{posix}}sed               # [win]
    - {{posix}}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-cluster
    - r-lattice
    - r-mvtnorm
    - r-pcapp
    - r-robustbase >=0.92.1
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{native}}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-cluster
    - r-lattice
    - r-mvtnorm
    - r-pcapp
    - r-robustbase >=0.92.1

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('rrcov')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('rrcov')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=rrcov
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Robust Location and Scatter Estimation and Robust Multivariate Analysis with High
    Breakdown Point.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r

# Maintainer: Valentin Todorov <valentin.todorov@chello.at>
